title: Gun used by 6-year-old who shot teacher in Virginia was 'secured,' family's lawyer says - USA TODAY
description: The family of the child who shot a teacher in Virginia said the gun used was "secured." Authorities haven't said how the 6-year-old got ahold of it.

title: Billions of celestial objects captured in new survey of the Milky Way - KSL.com
description: A new survey of the Milky Way galaxy has unveiled 3.3 billion celestial objects.

title: Pioneering Apple Lisa goes “open source” thanks to Computer History Museum - Ars Technica
description: Lisa OS 3.1's 1984 source Pascal code now available under a non-commercial license.
